                                    <img src="../images/solar/Jupiter.jpeg" alt="">
                                    <div class="solar-item__info">
                                        <h4 class="solar-item__name">Jupiter is the fifth planet from the Sun and is
                                            the largest planet in the solar system. If Jupiter were hollow, more than
                                            one thousand Earths could fit inside. It also contains two and a half times
                                            the mass of all the other planets combined. It has a mass of 1.9 x 1027 kg
                                            and is 142,800 kilometers (88,736 miles) across the equator.</h4>
                                        <h1>Jupiter Introduction</h1>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid__column-3_10">
                            <a href="#" class="solar-item">
                                <div class="solar-item__img">
                                    <img src="../images/solar/Saturn.png" alt="">
                                    <div class="solar-item__info">
                                        <h4 class="solar-item__name">Saturn is the sixth planet from the Sun and is the
                                            second largest in the solar system with an equatorial diameter of 119,300
                                            kilometers (74,130 miles). Much of what is known about the planet is due to
                                            the Voyager explorations in 1980-81. Saturn is visibly flattened at the
                                            poles, a result of the very fast rotation of the planet on its axis. Its
                                            day is 10 hours, 39 minutes long, and it takes 29.5 Earth years to revolve
                                            about the Sun.</h4>
                                        <h1>Saturn Introduction</h1>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        </div>
